        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Apple Intelligence 未來或會收費，外媒：或將採用月費制</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/apple-intelligence-4/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-intelligence-4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/apple-intelligence-4/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:00:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Intelligence]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1247561</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 可能計劃未來對其 AI 服務 Apple Intelligence 進行收費，以增加公司收入來源和減少對硬件銷售的依賴。Bloomberg 記者 Mark Gurman 報道指 Apple 的長期計劃包括向用户收費以使用更多 AI 功能。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple Intelligence 在上個月的全球開發者大會（WWDC）中亮相，功能包括 ChatGPT 整合、文本校對和重寫工具、新的 Siri 功能，以及生成圖像和表情符號等。Apple Intelligence 將於今年秋季聯同 iOS 18、iPadOS 18 和 macOS Sequoia 作業系統以測試版形式推出。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><strong> </strong></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">根據 Bloomberg 的報導，Apple 可能會推出一個名為 Apple Intelligence+ 的月度付費服務，將與 Apple 的其他數碼產品如 iCloud Plus、Apple TV Plus 和 Apple Fitness Plus 採取相似的模式。訂閲服務不只可以讓 Apple 從其龐大的 iPhone 用户基礎中獲得更多收益，更可以補充因全球智能手機出貨量下滑帶來的收入損失。雖然市場在 2024 年開始復甦，但根據國際數據公司（IDC）的數據，智能手機的總出貨量仍未達到以往水平。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.cnet.com/tech/mobile/apple-intelligence-may-eventually-cost-you/">Cnet</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/02/apple-intelligence-ai-paid/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 傳參照 iCloud+ 做法，部分 Apple Intelligence 功能將需要額外收費</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/01/gurman-apple-intelligence-coming-to-vision-pro/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《彭博》爆料 Apple Intelligence   將登陸 Vision Pro 但 HomePod 不獲支援</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/apple-intelligence-europe-delay/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Intelligence 歐盟延期推出　受「數碼市場法案」影響今年內不會提供</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/apple-intelligence-4/ai/">Apple Intelligence 未來或會收費，外媒：或將採用月費制</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/apple-intelligence-4/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Samsung Galaxy Unpacked 傳言大集合　6 個預計公佈重點</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-4/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-galaxy-unpacked-4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-4/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:00:08 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[潮流手錶]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音樂耳機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Buds3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Buds3 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Ring]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Unpacked]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Watch 7]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Watch Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Z Flip6]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Z Fold6]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Samsung Galaxy Z Fold]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1247509</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Samsung 即將於香港時間 7 月 10 日晚上 9 點於法國巴黎舉行 Galaxy Unpacked 發布會。隨著  Galaxy Unpacked 日子漸近，各大傳媒估計發布會有甚麼新產品，現在就讓小編分享一下外間有甚麼傳言吧！</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247512 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Unpacked 發布會</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Galaxy Z Fold6、Z Flip6 新機</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">有外媒表示，是次 Galaxy Unpacked 發布會的主角將會是新摺機 Galaxy Z Fold6 與 Z Flip6。知名爆料者 Evan Blass 預料 Galaxy Z Fold6 會有淺灰、深藍與粉紅三色，Galaxy Z Flip6 則會有淺灰、水藍、鵝黃與薄荷綠四色。規格方面，Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Z Flip 6 會採用與 S24 系列相同的 Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 處理器。暫時未知 Samsung 摺機處理器與相機是否會與 S24 系列相同，但 Samsung 曾證實將為摺機推出更強大的 Galaxy AI 體驗，值得期待一下。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247535 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-18-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-18-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-18.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Z Fold6（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.t3.com/news/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-6-and-z-flip-6-look-great-in-leaked-official-cases">t3</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247534 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-17-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-17-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-17.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Z Flip6（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.t3.com/news/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-6-and-z-flip-6-look-great-in-leaked-official-cases">t3</a>）</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Galaxy Watch 7</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">除了新摺機外， Samsung 會在發布會上推出新 Galaxy Watch 7 系列，將會推出 40mm 和 44mm 兩種尺寸，分別配備 1.3 吋和 1.5 吋螢幕。Galaxy Watch 7 有奶油白、銀色和深綠錶身搭配上同色波浪設計錶帶。Galaxy Watch7 擁有 2GB RAM 和 32GB 存儲空間，是上代 Galaxy Watch 6 的兩倍。電池容量方面，40mm 型號為 300mAh，44mm 型號為 425mAh，與現有型號相同。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247524 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-9-505x580.jpg" alt="" width="505" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-9-505x580.jpg 505w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-9.jpg 784w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 505px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247525 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-10-505x580.jpg" alt="" width="505" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-10-505x580.jpg 505w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-10.jpg 783w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 505px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247528 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-11-504x580.jpg" alt="" width="504" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-11-504x580.jpg 504w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-11.jpg 782w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 504px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Watch 7 傳聞售價：319 歐元（約港幣 HK$2,703）（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/more_renders_of_the_galaxy_unpacked_lineup_leak_ahead_of_launch-news-63490.php">Gsmarena</a>）</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/galaxy-watch-ultra-galaxy-watch7-series-price-leaked/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Galaxy Watch Ultra 定價曝光   Galaxy Watch7 系列與上代售價相若</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/02/galaxy-ring-skin-temperature-tracking-snore-detection/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Galaxy Ring 功能預覽，提供體温追蹤鼻鼾偵測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/01/galaxy-watch-ultra-leaked/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Galaxy Watch Ultra 產品照曝光，三色錶身錶帶配色選擇</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Galaxy Watch Ultra</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">除了全新的 Galaxy Watch 7 系列，Samsung 還會推出全新的 Samsung Galaxy Watch Ultra，期望會與 Apple Watch 高階款式競爭的 Wear OS 裝置。Galaxy Watch7 Ultra 有深灰、銀與橙色三種顏式。功能方面， Galaxy Watch Ultra 則與 Galaxy Watch 7 多方面相似，但錶殼尺寸增至 47mm，配備 1.5 吋螢幕，並標配 4G 連接，無藍牙專屬型號。電池容量亦有所增加，達到 590mAh，亦有可能同樣提供户外活動的高水準追蹤功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247529 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-12-503x580.jpg" alt="" width="503" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-12-503x580.jpg 503w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-12.jpg 781w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 503px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247530 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-13-502x580.jpg" alt="" width="502" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-13-502x580.jpg 502w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-13.jpg 779w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 502px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247531 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-14-505x580.jpg" alt="" width="505" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-14-505x580.jpg 505w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-14.jpg 784w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 505px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Watch Ultra 傳聞售價：699 歐元（約港幣 HK$5,931）（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/more_renders_of_the_galaxy_unpacked_lineup_leak_ahead_of_launch-news-63490.php">Gsmarena</a>）</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Galaxy Ring </strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Samsung 在 1 月的 S24 發布會上首次展示 Galaxy Ring，惟之後很少提及相關細節。是次發布會終於有望見到其全貌，與 Oura Ring 和 Ultrahuman Ring Air 等競爭產品相比，Galaxy Ring 將提供廣泛的健康和健身追蹤功能。據傳 Galaxy Ring 將有多種尺寸和款式選擇，並具備與 Galaxy Watch 類似的健康追蹤功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1247523 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-8-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-8-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-8.jpg 1196w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Ring（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.techradar.com/health-fitness/samsung-galaxy-ring-teased-at-unpacked-2024-heres-what-it-looks-like">Techradar</a>）</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Galaxy Buds3 與 Galaxy Buds3 Pro</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Samsung 都是時候更新真無線藍牙耳機，在發布會上會推出 Galaxy Buds3 及 Galaxy Buds3 Pro，分別都有白、銀灰兩隻顏色。Galaxy Buds3 會用上半入耳式設計，而 Galaxy Buds3 Pro 則會是入耳式設計。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247514 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-2-575x580.jpg" alt="" width="575" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-2-575x580.jpg 575w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-2.jpg 892w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-2-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 575px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247519 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-6-694x517.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="517" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-6-694x517.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-6.jpg 1207w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247520 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-7-694x515.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-7-694x515.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-7.jpg 1214w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247515 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-3-573x580.jpg" alt="" width="573" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-3-573x580.jpg 573w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-3.jpg 889w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 573px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247517 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-4-694x546.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="546" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-4-694x546.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-4.jpg 1143w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247518 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-5-694x556.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="556" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-5-694x556.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-5.jpg 1124w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Buds3 及 Galaxy Buds3 Pro（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.androidpolice.com/samsung-july-10-unpacked-event-what-to-expect/">Android Police</a>、<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/more_renders_of_the_galaxy_unpacked_lineup_leak_ahead_of_launch-news-63490.php">Gsmarena</a>）</p><h2>無平價版 Samsung Galaxy Z Fold</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">如果用家希望看到平價版的 Samsung Galaxy Z Fold，可能會失望了。據報導，Samsung 一直在研發一款經濟實惠的 Galaxy Z Fold，雖然缺少 S Pen 支援等功能，但提供更薄的機身和更大的螢幕。但由於生產延遲至 10 月，其發布可能要推遲到明年。即使平價版 Samsung Galaxy Z Fold 真的會推出，亦可能只會在中國和部分亞洲地區發售。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247513 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-1-694x459.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-1-694x459.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-1.jpg 1156w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Samsung 將不會發布平價版 Galaxy Z Fold（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.androidpolice.com/samsung-july-10-unpacked-event-what-to-expect/">Android Police</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.androidpolice.com/samsung-july-10-unpacked-event-what-to-expect/">Android Police</a>、<a href="https://www.techradar.com/health-fitness/smartwatches/massive-samsung-galaxy-watch-7-and-galaxy-watch-ultra-leak-reveals-their-full-specs">Techradar</a>、<a href="https://mashable.com/article/samsung-unpacked-july-2024-what-to-expect">Mashable</a>、<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/more_renders_of_the_galaxy_unpacked_lineup_leak_ahead_of_launch-news-63490.php">Gsmarena</a>、<a href="https://www.t3.com/news/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-6-and-z-flip-6-look-great-in-leaked-official-cases">t3</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/galaxy-watch-ultra-galaxy-watch7-series-price-leaked/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Galaxy Watch Ultra 定價曝光   Galaxy Watch7 系列與上代售價相若</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/02/galaxy-ring-skin-temperature-tracking-snore-detection/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Galaxy Ring 功能預覽，提供體温追蹤鼻鼾偵測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/01/galaxy-watch-ultra-leaked/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Galaxy Watch Ultra 產品照曝光，三色錶身錶帶配色選擇</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-4/mobile-phone/">Samsung Galaxy Unpacked 傳言大集合　6 個預計公佈重點</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
