            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Galaxy Watch Ultra 定價曝光   Galaxy Watch7 系列與上代售價相若</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/galaxy-watch-ultra-galaxy-watch7-series-price-leaked/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=galaxy-watch-ultra-galaxy-watch7-series-price-leaked</link>
